### Obtener todos los empleados
GET {{host}}/api/v1/employees
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Obtener un empleado por ID
GET {{host}}/api/v1/employees/1
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Crear un nuevo empleado
POST {{host}}/api/v1/employees
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "lastName": "García",
  "firstName": "Juan",
  "title": "Representante de Ventas",
  "titleOfCourtesy": "Sr.",
  "birthDate": "1990-05-15",
  "hireDate": "2023-01-10",
  "address": "Calle Falsa 123",
  "city": "Madrid",
  "region": "MD",
  "postalCode": "28001",
  "country": "España",
  "homePhone": "912345678",
  "extension": "123",
  "notes": "Empleado de prueba",
  "reportsToId": 1,
  "photoPath": "/photos/jgarcia.jpg"
}

### Actualización Parcial (PATCH) - Solo 1 o 2 campos
# Este ejemplo demuestra que los campos no enviados no se sobreescriben con null
PATCH {{host}}/api/v1/employees/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "lastName": "García Modificado",
  "title": "Gerente de Ventas"
}

### Actualización Total (PUT)
PUT {{host}}/api/v1/employees/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "lastName": "García",
  "firstName": "Juan",
  "title": "Representante de Ventas",
  "titleOfCourtesy": "Sr.",
  "birthDate": "1990-05-15",
  "hireDate": "2023-01-10",
  "address": "Calle Real 456",
  "city": "Madrid",
  "region": "MD",
  "postalCode": "28001",
  "country": "España",
  "homePhone": "912345678",
  "extension": "123",
  "notes": "Empleado de prueba con dirección actualizada",
  "reportsToId": 1,
  "photoPath": "/photos/jgarcia.jpg"
}

### Eliminar un empleado
DELETE {{host}}/api/v1/employees/1
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Obtener detalles agrupados de empleados
GET {{host}}/api/v1/employee-details
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
